nd her son &quot;? </div><div class="t m1ff9 x73 h2b y90f ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What, then, is the exhortation given? </div><div class="t m12cd x73 h2b y127f ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Have you the freedom of Christ? </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
